sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Go 应用
    participant P as Producer
    participant AP as Proxy接入点
    participant Cache as 路由缓存
    participant B1 as Broker/Proxy A
    participant B2 as Broker/Proxy B

    App->>P: Send(message)
    P->>Cache: 查询 Topic 路由
    alt 缓存未命中
        P->>AP: QueryRoute(topic)
        AP-->>P: MessageQueue 列表
        P->>Cache: 缓存路由
    end
    P->>P: 选择候选队列/Endpoint
    P->>B1: SendMessage
    alt 成功
        B1-->>P: SendReceipt
    else 超时或错误且未达最大尝试次数
        P->>P: 隔离失败 Endpoint
        P->>B2: 重试同一业务消息
        B2-->>P: SendReceipt 或 error
    end
    P-->>App: receipt 或最终错误
